data.name: descriptionLabel.Text
data.value:
"BlackJack" is a common card game played in casinos. If you don't know how to play BlackJack, Google it.
"Ride the Bus" is mainly a college drinking game. If you also don't know how to play this one, Google it.
Anyway, I did my best to recreate these games in my beloved C# language. I used ChatGPT to help me with the UI layout and a majority of the game logic.
Also, I disabled any form of betting/saving scores. I don't want anyone playing this game to develop a habit of gambling! Gambling is not a joke and has ruined many lives. I want these game recreations to be friendly and non-competitive. They should only be played for fun. ___________________________________________________________________________
